When I try to remove Warning( Accessing createClass via the main React package is deprecated) from my app with version React 15.6.x and as per https://fb.me/react-create-class steps. 
I have included 'create-react-class' as npm package in my React app and made according changes in my React component, but it is giving me below mentioned serialize TypeError : 

**error TypeError: Serializing native function: bound onceWrapper
    at ../node_modules/serialize-javascript/index.js:114:19
    at String.replace (<anonymous>)
    at serialize (/Users/jgohil/Mobi-projects/ortus-web/node_modules/serialize-javascript/index.js:101:16)**
<img width="1315" alt="screen shot 2018-05-14 at 17 35 01" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16350637/39996447-2731fda2-579d-11e8-8b2e-7c73573055fe.png">

Can you please help me out what is missing in my code or what is going wrong ?

Below is my component code as per new 'create-react-class'  guidelines as after I changed : 

Below is code of my main rendering component of React SSR application i.e.  : Html.js 

```
import React, { PropTypes } from 'react';
import Component from 'create-react-class';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/server';
import serialize from 'serialize-javascript';
import Helmet from 'react-helmet';;

var Html = Component({
  propTypes : {
    ....
  },

  render() {
    const { bundle } = this.props;
    const content = component ? ReactDOM.renderToString(component) : '';
    const head = Helmet.rewind();

    return (
      <html lang="nl">
        <head> 
                  ....
        </head>
        <body>
          <div id="content" dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: content }} />
          <script dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{__html: `window.__data=${ serialize(store.getState()) };`}} charSet="UTF-8"/>
          <script async type="text/javascript" src={ `${bundle}` } charSet="UTF-8" />
          
        </body>
      </html>
    )
  }
 });

export default Html;
```

I want to remove  these deprecation warnings from my app(React 15.6.x) without upgrading to React 16.x.  Can you please help me in removing these errors ?
